All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Ballot
A Ballot represents a ballot in an IR election with the candidates ranked.
BallotTest
BallotTest class contains test methods for the Ballot class.
Candidate
A Candidate represents a candidate in an IR election.
CandidateTest
CandidateTest class contains methods for testing the Candidate class.
CPLProcessing
CPLProcessing.java This file implements a CPLProcessing class that is responsible for handling a CPL election.
CPLProcessingTest
CPLProcessingTest class contains methods for testing the CPLProcessing class.
IElectionProcessing
IElectionProcessing interface provides an outline for an election processing class.
IRepresentative
IRepresentative interface provides the outline for a representative class.
IRProcessing
IRProcessing class used for processing an IR election.
IRProcessingTest
IRProcessingTest class contains methods for testing the IRProcessing class.
IRRow
Class for holding IR table data for each candidate.
IRRowTest
Contains methods for testing the IRRow class.
main
main class where user will be prompted for election information file and election system will be run.
MainTest
MainTest class contains test methods for the main method.
Party
The Party class creates Party objects that represent political parties in a CPL election.
PartyTest
PartyTest class contains methods for testing the Party class.
POProcessing
POProcessing class used for processing a PO election.
POProcessingTest
POProcessingTest class contains methods for testing the POProcessing class.
ProcessResults
ProcessResults is used in election processing to write election results and proceedings to an audit file.
